<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Am</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Iso mening Rabbimdur
 Unda bordur hayot nuri
 Ulugʻlayman doimo
 Barhayot Otamni

[C1]
   Kuylayin nomingga sanolar
   Inoyatingda men yashnab
   Aytay Senga men sanolar
   Mehringdan men quvonib

[V2]
 Sevgi toʻla mehringdan
 Huzuringda kuylayin
 Hamdlar aytib nomingga
 Toʻxtamasdan kuylayin Ota

[V3]
 Akkord:
. Am   Em
 Akkord
. Dm   G
 Akkord
. Am   Em
 Akkord
. F    G
 Akkord</lyrics>
<title>Iso mening Rabbimdur</title>
<author>Ali Ergashev, Ulugʻbek Joʻrayev</author>
</song>